# 🚀 Space Satellite Tracker

A full-stack AI-powered system for tracking satellites and predicting space debris collisions.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* Frontend: React.js
* Backend: Python (Flask)
* Database: MySQL
* Visualization: Charts + UI Dashboard

## ⚙️ Setup

### 1. Start MySQL (XAMPP)

### 2. Run Backend

```bash
cd backend
venv\Scripts\activate
python app.py
```

### 3. Run Frontend

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

### 🌐 Access

http://localhost:5173
